The 2018 Asian Continental Championship is a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 10-18 December in Makati City, Philippines.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.philchesstournaments.com
